quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  67,1,"Mo laamu woni e juu…óe mum mawnii, ko KaŇčko woni kattan…óo kala hu'unde."
  67,2,"Oon tagir…óo maayde e nguurndam, fii ndaarndagol on ko hommbo e mo'on …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude golle. Ko KaŇčko woni poolu…óo, kaforoowo on."
  67,3,"On tak…óo kammuuji jee…ói…ói pawondir…ói. A yi'ataa …ďura-…ďurda e tagoore jom hinaraŇčke On. Yiiltu ndaar…óe maa …óen (daaraa). Taw si a yi'ay ce'ekol?"
  67,4,"Refti nduttaa ndaar…óe …óen laa…ďi …ói…ói, gite maa …óeen nduttoto e maa…óa hara ko …óe hoy…óe, ta∆īii…óe."
  67,5,"GooŇč…óii Min cu…óinirii kammu aduna nguun [koode] pitilli, Min mba…ói …óe fi…óir…óe seytanuuji, Min kebilani …ďe lette hu…ď…ďunge nge."
  67,6,"Hino woodani …ďeen yeddu…ďe Joomi mum, lette Jahannama. Nge bonii ruttorde !"
  67,7,"Si …ďe mbeddaama e ndeer magge, …ďe nanirat nge ha'acaango, hara henge fata."
  67,8,"Henge e…ď…ďa fultagol, sabu tikkere ndeen. Tuma kala nde dental bugaa e magge, ayninaa…ďe nge …ďeen lamndoo …ďe : ""E hara jeertinoowo araano e mo'on?"""
  67,9,"∆Āe mbi'a: ""Pellet ! Jeertinoowo arno e amen tigi, kono min njeddi min mbi'i: Allah jippinaani hay e hu'unde, on ngonaani si wonaa e ndeer majjere mawnde""."
  67,10,"∆Āe mbi'ita : ""Si mi…óen nanaynoo maa hara me…óen haqqilaynoo, min njeyetanooke e yim…ďe Hu…ď…ďunge ngeen""."
  67,11,"∆Āe qirritii bakkatuuji ma…ď…ďe …óin. Halakuyee woodanii joom en Hu…ď…ďaynge ngen."
  67,12,"Pellet, huloo…ďe Joomi mum …ďeen ka wirnii, hino woodani …ďen haforaneede e njo…ďdi mawndi."
  67,13,"Cuu…óee konngu…ói mon maa …ďanninon …óum. KaŇčko on ko o ganndu…óo ko woni e ndeer …ďer…óe."
  67,14,"E hara tak…óo oon anndaa? Ko KaŇčko le woni newii…óo, kumpitii…óo oon."
  67,15,"Ko KaŇčko wa…óani on leydi ndin eeltaandi : haray njehee e seraaji mayri, √Īaamon e arsike makko. Ko ka makko woni ummital ngal."
  67,16,"E on kooli on gon'…óo ka kammu nde o munnataa e mo'on leydi ndin, tawa yoo hindi dilla?"
  67,17,"Kaa on kooli On gon'…óo ka kammu nde Oo wurtataa e mon henndu bippooru? Aray nde anndon ko honno woni jeertinaango am ngon."
  67,18,"Sellii adinoo…ďe …ďeen …óoon …ďen njeddiino. Taskii ko honno le…ďte an …óen mbattinirnoo!"
  67,19,"E …ďee nji'aani colli …óiin dow ma…ď…ďe, hi…ói fonta gabitannji …ói √Īobba? [Won'de] jogitaaki …óin si wonaa Joom hinaraŇčke on. Pellet, ko o deen…óo kala hu'unde."
  67,20,"E ko hommbo woni on konuujo mum wallata on hara wonaa Jom hinaraŇčke on? Tigi on, he'efer…ďe …ďeen ngonaani si wonaa e ndeer hodo."
  67,21,"E ko hommbo woni arsikoowo on, si o jogitike arsike makko on? si ko woni, …ďe duumike e ∆īaggere e go…ó…óitagol."
  67,22,"Kere ko on jahoowo no hippi ye'eso mum …ďuri feewde? Kaa ko on jahoowo no fotondiri e laawol pocciingol?"
  67,23,"Maaku: ""Ko KaŇčko woni ko fu…ó…ói oon, O wa…óani on nan…óe e gii…óe e …ďer…óe"". Kono fam…óii ko njettoton [neema]."
  67,24,"Maaku: ""Ko KaŇčko woni ca'aktu…óo on leydi, ko ka makko kadi woni ko moo…ďitoyte…óon""."
  67,25,"He…ďe mbi'a: ""Ko honnde tuma woni ndee fodoore, si tawii ko on gooŇč…óu…ďe?"""
  67,26,"Maaku : ""nganndee anndugol [fii Darnagl] ko ka Allah woni. Miiin on ko Mi jeertinoowo [tan] …ďanngina""."
  67,27,"Nde …ďe nji'oyta (le…ďte) …óen ka …ďadii, j'eece yeddu…ďe …ďen suni j'eece he'efer…ďe, […ďe] mbi'anee : ""Ko …óuum …óoo woni ko …óa…ď…ďatno…óon""."
  67,28,"Maaku : ""Yeetee kam, si Allah ∆īettitii kam miin e wonndii…ďe am maa o yurmaama min, ko hommbo da…óndata he'efer…ďe …ďeen lepte mu'usuu…óe?"""
  67,29,"Maaku : ""Ko KaŇčko Joom hinaraŇčke oon. Min ngooŇč…óinii mo, ko e makko kadi men fawii. Aray nde nganndon ko hommbo woni e majjere …ďanngunde""."
  67,30,"Maaku : ""njeewtee kam , si ndiyam mon …óam wattinii …ďee…ďu…óam, ko hommbo addanta on ndiyam ilat…óam?"""
